      	<article allWordsNum="122">
            	<![CDATA[
Is travel about to change forever? Elon Musk, an American inventor, has come up with a new design for a super-fast transport system.
The transport system will have pods (分离舱) for people to sit in. The pods will travel through a tube. Musk said that the whole system could run on solar power (太阳能) and the ticket would cost only $20.
The pods will hold about 28 people and travel at up to 760 miles per hour. People can travel from Los Angeles to San Francisco (旧金山) in just 30 minutes! It usually takes 75 minutes by plane or around five-and-a-half hours by car to go between the two cities.
Musk said that the system would be a faster, safer and cheaper mode of transport.
          	]]>
            </article>
